OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 25 JUN
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1967FOur World - the first live,
OL,7,Finternational, satellite television
OL,8,Fproduction - airs on BBC One. The Radio
OL,9,FTimes listing reads: "The European
OL,10,FBroadcasting Union, in association with
OL,11,Fthe television services of eighteen
OL,12,Fnations, presents Our World. This
OL,13,Fevening in Europe, this afternoon in
OL,14,FAmerica, tomorrow in Japan, live
OL,15,Ftelevision circles the globe for the
OL,16,Ffirst time ever, linking five
OL,17,Fcontinents and bringing man
OL,18,Fface-to-face with mankind in places as
OL,19,Ffar apart as Canberra and Cape Kennedy,
OL,20,FMoscow and Montreal, Samarkand and
OL,21,FSoderfors, Takamatsu and Tunis."
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
